  <content contentuid="h4e865d84g44afg68b5gc703g6354ae84e523" version="2">When an enemy dies within 15 ft of you, you empower your weapon with that creature's soul's energy. Your next weapon attack does necrotic damage equal to half your fighter level.</content>
